{"id":307843,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/08/维权网-各地维权人士外交部声援要求参加国家人/","date":"2013-08-07T05:18:40Z","modified":"2013-08-07T05:18:40Z","title":"维权网 | 各地维权人士外交部声援要求参加国家人权报告编撰的公民（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员田静民报道）北京的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月天气酷暑难耐，但自</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日开始，由北京维权人士曹顺利等人发起的中国公民运动团体在外交部大门口静坐。公民要求参加《人权报告》撰写活动至今已</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">48</span><span>天，坚守在外交部门前的参与者们，仍在等候着外交部的关于公民要求参加人权报告撰写及要求信息公开的答复。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">48</span><span>天来，无论刮风下雨、炎热酷暑，还是警方干预，都没能阻止在此坚守的公民。本来是在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">22</span><span>日</span><span>结束的人权活动，只因为公民们对中国人权的渴望和执着硬是在炎热的酷暑中把活动坚持下来。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>大家的坚守赢得各界人士的关注和声援。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日，来自吉林、辽宁、天津、河南、上海、广西等地的维权访民，前往外交部声援在此昼夜坚守、为了促进人权进步而等待外交部答复的公民们。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>参加声援的各地维权人士唯一的要求就是事实求是的把中国的人权状况写入历史史册，以改变中国权大于法的现状。确实兑现习近平所讲的把权力关进笼子里，实现法治社会，让公民享有真正的权利。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>参加声援活动的有：上海吴玉芬、沈丽秀、吉林邓志波、辽宁赵广军、林明杰、王素饿、杨秀梅、天津郑建慧、毋秀玲、河南李玉凤、黑龙江张宝珠等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>余人。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-crVNmtUaNq4/UgHDFnJEDDI/AAAAAAAAmbE/DkOnksEaQCU/s1600/2013-08-06+14.38.35.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"211\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-crVNmtUaNq4/UgHDFnJEDDI/AAAAAAAAmbE/DkOnksEaQCU/s320/2013-08-06+14.38.35.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-GXSKvI1M42Y/UgHDFyOJY5I/AAAAAAAAmbI/8FcVK12SzHA/s1600/2013-08-06+15.31.10.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"234\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-GXSKvI1M42Y/UgHDFyOJY5I/AAAAAAAAmbI/8FcVK12SzHA/s320/2013-08-06+15.31.10.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}